import { Input } from "@chakra-ui/react"

export default function Busqueda() {
    return (
        <InputGroup>
            <InputLeftElement
                pointerEvents='none'
                color='gray.300'
                fontSize='1.2em'
                children='$'
            />
            <Input placeholder='Enter amount' />
            <InputRightElement>
                <CheckIcon color='green.500' />
            </InputRightElement>
        </InputGroup>
    );
}
